## Objective
The app should allow a user to enter any topic and have that topic generate flashcards with questions and answers related to that topic to help the user learn.

## Information Architecture
### Dashboard (Home)
Recent decks (stored in localStorage), “Continue studying” CTA, global search, New Deck button

### New Deck (Source Input)
Tabs: Paste Text | Markdown 
Options: target deck size, difficulty, Bloom level (remember/understand/apply), format (Q/A, cloze, MCQ).

### Deck Detail
Cards list - review, replace, delete, add, edit.

### Study Session
Card view; user grades (Again/Hard/Good/Easy); progress bar;
